---
const struggles = [
  'Lust',
  'Money Matters',
  'Fatherhood',
  'Marriage',
  'Pornography',
  'Addiction',
  'Adultery',
  'Anger',
  'Depression',
  "Caring For Loved Ones with afflictions or disease like Alzheimer's or Dementia.",
];
---
<section id="brotherhood" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-gray-900 text-center">Brotherhood Support</h2>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p>Do you have questions about your faith? Do you know who you are as a Christian man?</p>
      <p>Are you struggling or feel trapped and have regret from things you've done, people you've hurt and where you are in life?</p>
      <p>What about the thorns that bother you and you just can't seem to shake?</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3">
      {struggles.map((s) => (
        <li class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm sm:text-base font-medium text-gray-800 shadow-sm">{s}</li>
      ))}
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p>Maybe you're haunted by something from your past that still keeps you up at night.</p>
      <p>Do you ever question God's forgiveness or your righteousness in HIM?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <p class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-[var(--color-brand-red)]">STOP WALKING ALONE</p>
      <a href="https://hyppohq.io/f/join-the-brotherhood?theme=light" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold text-white bg-[var(--color-brand-red)] hover:opacity-90 transition">Join The Brotherhood</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
